01:07:40.267 --> 01:07:43.817
What does this company do, ie, what's the sector?

01:07:44.236 --> 01:07:48.166
The sector is fashion and textile, mother, they make clothes.

01:07:49.226 --> 01:07:51.476
How long have they been established? Are they stable?

01:07:54.840 --> 01:07:57.198
This year they have their 40th anniversary.

01:07:58.755 --> 01:08:01.465
They certainly will have a celebration for the 40 years.

01:08:03.055 --> 01:08:03.912
That is possible.

01:08:08.771 --> 01:08:10.041
What is their profit like?

01:08:12.164 --> 01:08:14.806
I mean, what value do their stocks have?

01:08:16.727 --> 01:08:25.854
I mean, have they invested? What are their dreams? Tell me which way next?

01:08:27.569 --> 01:08:28.934
Why are you laughing?

01:08:29.777 --> 01:08:31.899
How could I not laugh, aunt Fadik?

01:08:32.725 --> 01:08:35.897
I didn't buy the company, I just work there.

01:08:36.759 --> 01:08:45.410
My daughter, my child, don't say that. If the company goes bankrupt, you'll be jobless.

01:08:46.112 --> 01:08:47.943
I mean, your father asks, that's why I asked.

01:08:49.773 --> 01:08:55.725
He asked me about the profit margin and said we should reconsider after looking at stock prices.

01:08:56.279 --> 01:09:06.563
Tell him Hayat said 'Don't worry, she has a great job which she could lose tomorrow because you questioned me.

01:09:07.343 --> 01:09:08.399
Ok good night.

01:09:14.668 --> 01:09:15.654
She's right.

01:11:50.517 --> 01:11:51.746
Look, be strong...

01:11:51.863 --> 01:11:55.445
But do not let anyone crush you. Do what you need to do at work, but don't over work.

01:11:55.753 --> 01:11:57.604
Browse for your rights, but don't you dare....

01:11:57.615 --> 01:11:58.930
get fired

01:11:59.160 --> 01:12:02.229
As your father said that he will not give you another chance if you get fired.

01:12:02.260 --> 01:12:04.281
And he said he would come and take you here and that's it.

01:12:06.460 --> 01:12:07.921
And what do you say, Mom?

01:12:09.299 --> 01:12:10.750
What should I say, my daughter?

01:12:10.978 --> 01:12:14.350
No, I mean what do you expect from me?

01:12:15.063 --> 01:12:16.355
What could I expect, my girl?

01:12:16.557 --> 01:12:19.525
I want you to be good, healthy and happy.

01:12:19.533 --> 01:12:21.079
What else can a mother want?

01:12:22.971 --> 01:12:25.461
But if I go back there, I wont be fine and happy mother.

01:12:25.739 --> 01:12:28.575
Do not get me wrong, I'm not saying this because I look down at that place.

01:12:28.582 --> 01:12:29.883
I love my hometown.

01:12:31.466 --> 01:12:35.105
But if I go back there, it is clear of the life that is waiting for me.

01:12:40.600 --> 01:12:43.387
At least, that's not the life I dream of.

01:12:44.842 --> 01:12:46.521
That life is not this life, Mom.

01:12:48.778 --> 01:12:50.489
At least, don't do that to me.

01:12:53.982 --> 01:12:55.689
Come here.

01:13:01.635 --> 01:13:04.498
My child... my child.

01:13:09.074 --> 01:13:10.075
Okay, okay.

01:13:10.911 --> 01:13:12.169
I promise I will not be fired.

01:13:12.359 --> 01:13:14.374
Say hi to Dad for me, okay?

01:13:14.461 --> 01:13:15.203
I'm late!

01:13:15.662 --> 01:13:17.102
I'm really late!

01:13:22.923 --> 01:13:24.374
Why did not you wake me up?

01:13:25.452 --> 01:13:27.920
What happened to her?

01:13:28.342 --> 01:13:29.273
She overslept.

01:13:31.865 --> 01:13:32.506
Come on.

01:13:35.149 --> 01:13:38.331
My beautiful daughter.

01:13:39.200 --> 01:13:40.306
See you.

01:14:22.967 --> 01:14:24.030
Miss Suna?

01:14:26.492 --> 01:14:27.678
I said Suna.

01:14:28.583 --> 01:14:30.156
Are you talking to me?

01:14:30.622 --> 01:14:32.909
Is there any other Suna's here?

01:14:33.420 --> 01:14:35.207
I do not know, probably not I guess.

01:14:35.665 --> 01:14:37.917
Mr. Nejat waiting for you in his office.

01:14:38.003 --> 01:14:38.821
Mr. Nejat?

01:14:40.146 --> 01:14:41.541
Nejat Sarslimaz.

01:14:41.905 --> 01:14:45.966
Big boss, the one who is your dad's friend?

01:14:47.620 --> 01:14:48.359
That's right!

01:14:49.319 --> 01:14:50.449
Mr. Nejat...

01:14:51.629 --> 01:14:52.854
Nejat uncle...

01:14:53.497 --> 01:14:55.176
He is my father's friend.

01:14:55.637 --> 01:14:56.860
The office is in the last room in the corridor.

01:14:58.679 --> 01:15:05.162
Would not it be better to establish me in my office first, to know my colleagues?

01:15:05.847 --> 01:15:08.989
I mean, it's not a good first impression to the boss, if I seem so free.

01:15:10.043 --> 01:15:11.217
No, you can not.

01:15:12.498 --> 01:15:15.160
I mean, you can not postpone it. He wanted to see you as soon as you came.

01:15:19.435 --> 01:15:21.127
So it is required.

01:15:23.547 --> 01:15:25.414
There is no escape, I suppose.

01:15:28.975 --> 01:15:31.128
Okay, then I'll go.

01:15:32.073 --> 01:15:33.023
From here?

01:15:33.941 --> 01:15:35.018
From here.

01:15:40.607 --> 01:15:42.856
I don't know what is going on in her head.

01:15:52.139 --> 01:15:53.776
Welcome, Mr. Murat.

01:15:56.136 --> 01:15:57.215
Are these the new ones?

01:15:57.492 --> 01:15:58.425
Yes, sir.

01:16:00.183 --> 01:16:01.610
Did you organise a meeting with the designers?

01:16:01.625 --> 01:16:03.263
Yes sir, they will be here at 11.

01:16:03.349 --> 01:16:04.580
Bring me a double espresso.

01:16:04.596 --> 01:16:05.700
Before breakfast, sir?

01:16:06.102 --> 01:16:08.400
If I wanted breakfast, I'd ask. Do you understand Cagla?

01:16:12.322 --> 01:16:14.736
How nice, we will be tortured by you today.

01:16:22.312 --> 01:16:23.590
Help me, Lord.

01:16:25.476 --> 01:16:27.018
Come in, please.

01:16:30.266 --> 01:16:31.445
Come, my girl.

01:16:32.647 --> 01:16:35.635
So you're Kemal's daughter?

01:16:36.771 --> 01:16:39.067
It is something you could say, yes.

01:16:40.316 --> 01:16:41.862
Just like her father, great!

01:16:42.577 --> 01:16:43.534
Come, sit down.

01:16:43.987 --> 01:16:45.675
I do not want to bother you.

01:16:45.881 --> 01:16:51.249
Why would you bother me, my daughter, come and talk to me a little about your father.

01:16:53.281 --> 01:16:54.198
so...

01:16:55.224 --> 01:16:56.644
We couldn't talk much on the phone.

01:16:57.512 --> 01:16:58.894
Tell me, what is he doing?

01:16:59.946 --> 01:17:02.299
Actually... I ..

01:17:02.725 --> 01:17:04.719
But how would you know, right?

01:17:05.199 --> 01:17:07.980
He's spent most of the year in Cape Town, how great!

01:17:13.572 --> 01:17:14.499
So what?

01:17:15.077 --> 01:17:16.742
How much longer until he retires?

01:17:18.304 --> 01:17:19.506
Wait, what did he say?

01:17:19.873 --> 01:17:21.410
He said something like this year being his last.

01:17:22.632 --> 01:17:23.681
So it seems.

01:17:25.170 --> 01:17:32.264
He should remarry. Derya and I have said many times, after your mother died, but he refuses.

01:17:33.157 --> 01:17:34.482
He has lived his life alone.

01:17:35.167 --> 01:17:39.047
Is it not normal when the pain of losing my mother is so fresh?

01:17:39.883 --> 01:17:41.407
20 years have passed, my girl.

01:17:42.331 --> 01:17:43.161
Is that so?

01:17:46.162 --> 01:17:47.882
Has it been so long?

01:17:49.250 --> 01:17:52.030
Time flies so fast, Uncle Nejat.

01:17:52.789 --> 01:17:53.730
That is true.

01:17:54.601 --> 01:17:59.366
For example, I have not seen since you were 5 years.

01:18:01.385 --> 01:18:03.455
But before, were you not blonde?

01:18:03.498 --> 01:18:05.957
Oh this! It's dye. I'm still blonde.

01:18:08.009 --> 01:18:12.080
Anyway, I will not bother you anymore and anger your boss.

01:18:13.341 --> 01:18:14.757
My boss?

01:18:16.125 --> 01:18:17.987
Your father never told you?

01:18:19.007 --> 01:18:22.012
I'm slowly leaving all my work for my sons

01:18:28.805 --> 01:18:34.755
So he's grumpy again. If he won't throw this espresso at me, I'll be surprised.

01:18:35.263 --> 01:18:36.109
Miss Suna!

01:18:37.167 --> 01:18:39.118
Perfect, perfect timing.

01:18:39.989 --> 01:18:41.318
Mr Murat awaits you.

01:18:41.866 --> 01:18:43.539
Come one after another.

01:18:46.665 --> 01:18:47.983
Who is Mr. Murat?

01:18:48.237 --> 01:18:49.839
The elder son of Mr. Nejat.

01:18:49.990 --> 01:18:54.033
He's very sweet. In fact, in the mornings, he's like a marshmallow.

01:18:54.995 --> 01:18:57.461
He asked for an espresso. I thought you could start there.

01:18:57.549 --> 01:18:59.346
In fact from now, this is your job.

01:18:59.495 --> 01:19:00.938
The room opposite here.

01:19:01.205 --> 01:19:02.967
Hurry, hurry, run.

01:19:03.840 --> 01:19:04.610
Run.

01:19:16.175 --> 01:19:16.801
Enter.

01:19:19.092 --> 01:19:20.315
You can put it on the table, Cagla.

01:19:21.066 --> 01:19:24.264
Cagla, I mean, Ms. Cagla asked me to bring me coffee.

01:19:55.651 --> 01:19:58.192
Enough. This is too much.

01:19:58.668 --> 01:19:59.694
What are you doing here?

01:20:00.284 --> 01:20:01.853
I've told you, this is my work place.

01:20:02.035 --> 01:20:04.549
I understand that much. What are you doing in Mr Murat's office?

01:20:04.906 --> 01:20:07.402
What are these positions, hands in pockets, in front of the window?

01:20:08.534 --> 01:20:09.544
I'm Murat.

01:20:09.857 --> 01:20:13.615
And so what? If you ask 10 people on the street, two of them will say they are Murat.

01:20:14.545 --> 01:20:19.119
Just because you have the same name, does not mean you can enter the boss's office.

01:20:23.319 --> 01:20:33.309
Oh. You, I mean, you're that Murat.

01:20:36.405 --> 01:20:37.720
Murat the boss.

01:20:41.196 --> 01:20:43.720
Exactly, can you give me my coffee now?

01:20:46.872 --> 01:20:48.448
I apologize.

01:20:48.980 --> 01:20:50.714
I'm really sorry.

01:20:51.695 --> 01:20:54.905
If I knew, I would not be so...

01:20:55.195 --> 01:20:57.158
But you didn't make it obvious that you were Mr Murat.

01:20:58.393 --> 01:21:00.095
Thanks for the warning.

01:21:00.808 --> 01:21:04.602
From now on, I'll walk around, telling everyone I am Murat Sarsilmaz.

01:21:05.435 --> 01:21:07.080
No, that's not what I meant.

01:21:07.340 --> 01:21:08.468
Well, the discussion is over.

01:21:08.549 --> 01:21:09.432
Suna, right?

01:21:09.501 --> 01:21:10.316
No, Hayat.

01:21:11.813 --> 01:21:12.366
How?

01:21:13.166 --> 01:21:16.285
I mean, my name legally is Suna Pektas.

01:21:17.164 --> 01:21:19.994
In my private life, I prefer to be called Hayat.

01:21:21.301 --> 01:21:22.682
My father does not know.

01:21:23.241 --> 01:21:26.005
I don't want him to think I don't like the name he gave me.

01:21:28.580 --> 01:21:29.823
Okay, let's not extend this.

01:21:29.859 --> 01:21:30.717
Yeah sure.

01:21:32.069 --> 01:21:35.373
The fact that you got this job because of your father means nothing to me.

01:21:35.587 --> 01:21:38.222
Indifference is what I hate the workplace.

01:21:38.438 --> 01:21:41.490
Therefore, in my eyes, you're not Suna Pektas, but simply an employee.

01:21:41.787 --> 01:21:42.973
That's exactly what I am.

01:21:43.066 --> 01:21:44.418
Please do not cut me off while I'm talking.

01:21:50.101 --> 01:21:50.868
Yes.

01:21:52.661 --> 01:21:53.299
Yes, what?

01:21:53.994 --> 01:21:56.295
You said not to cut you off, and stopped talking.

01:21:56.526 --> 01:21:58.165
Oh, so you can't do work without an order.

01:21:58.927 --> 01:22:00.382
You can leave now.

01:22:16.689 --> 01:22:20.805
So, said epitome of selfishness, polar bear, turned out to be my boss, Asli, look at what you're saying.

01:22:21.176 --> 01:22:25.693
Why are you upset? I'm just saying that every great romance begins with a fight.

01:22:25.694 --> 01:22:30.344
Well, that was used in a sense of chasing. It's been hundreds of years since that saying was used darling.

01:22:30.346 --> 01:22:34.624
In Hayat's case, she will end up chasing after him, he is her boss. It will be bad

01:22:34.813 --> 01:22:38.667
Thanks, girls, you're being really useful. What am I supposed to do now?

01:22:38.840 --> 01:22:42.411
It's not just a lie, but suffering that is connected to this job. I say quit.

01:22:42.570 --> 01:22:48.252
Don't you dare Hayat. You know what will happen if you do.

01:22:48.311 --> 01:22:50.372
Living a life with a lie is wrong.

01:22:50.372 --> 01:22:53.339
Life is wrong without lies anyway.

01:22:53.593 --> 01:22:59.424
Also, there is no such thing as a good boss, only hard working employees.

01:23:04.030 --> 01:23:06.651
You're exactly and hour and a half late for the rehearsal.

01:23:07.657 --> 01:23:09.933
And you care only care about makeup, darling Didem?

01:23:10.363 --> 01:23:13.014
Look at me, Tuval, for God's sake, look at me.

01:23:13.206 --> 01:23:14.367
Turn, let me see.

01:23:14.437 --> 01:23:14.976
Look.

01:23:17.869 --> 01:23:18.494
Yes.

01:23:19.456 --> 01:23:23.066
You really look like a rotten model that was forgotten in the warehouse.

01:23:23.477 --> 01:23:26.541
Thanks, Tuval, you're really morale.

01:23:27.181 --> 01:23:29.877
I do not work in team morale.

01:23:30.440 --> 01:23:37.764
I'm chief designer of this great company, I'm with you right now because I want to do my work on time.

01:23:38.246 --> 01:23:41.444
There is no way I can face people like this.

01:23:41.983 --> 01:23:44.097
Do not push me, Tuval. I'm very tired, do not push me.

01:23:45.861 --> 01:23:49.941
Tell me what happened? Did you carry a heavy weighing bag in the morning?

01:23:51.082 --> 01:23:55.678
Last night I was at Murat's home. We slept really late.

01:23:57.222 --> 01:24:06.475
I'm not interested in your private life. I don't think it concerns Murat either. If you can try on this seasons creations before the next season, it would be great.

01:24:14.469 --> 01:24:16.645
So what are you going to do?

01:24:17.184 --> 01:24:21.325
First I'm going to wash my face with cold water. I think my blood pressure rose.

01:24:21.353 --> 01:24:26.964
And tell your boss "mmm, you may look fine, but you have no personality."

01:24:27.300 --> 01:24:32.003
Don't you dare ruin your decency. Besides, who are you to judge someone's personality?

01:24:32.234 --> 01:24:33.754
All right, girls, I'm closing the phone.

01:24:40.662 --> 01:24:42.721
Honey, can you give me two tissues, please?

01:24:48.691 --> 01:24:51.925
Simply put them on my neck, I don't want powder everywhere.

01:24:56.376 --> 01:24:57.228
Merci.

01:24:59.852 --> 01:25:02.515
Slowly, I don't want to get water to splash my dress

01:25:04.491 --> 01:25:05.645
Do you have any other orders?

01:25:06.380 --> 01:25:13.272
I did not have breakfast. Get me fresh orange juice and yogurt with cereal, but no fruit pieces.

01:25:13.527 --> 01:25:15.747
For god's sake, look at you.

01:25:15.827 --> 01:25:17.309
I can't look, my mascara hasn't dried.

01:25:20.200 --> 01:25:21.371
Hurry! What are you waiting for?

01:25:21.882 --> 01:25:23.465
Do you know who I am?

01:25:25.685 --> 01:25:26.363
No.

01:25:27.679 --> 01:25:30.265
Murat Sarslimaz's assistant's assistant.

01:25:31.283 --> 01:25:35.241
Is that so? I'm Murat Sarsilmaz's girlfriend.

01:25:35.870 --> 01:25:40.402
To my knowledge, there is no position of being the 'boss's girlfriend'.

01:25:40.648 --> 01:25:43.607
I am also the face of this company, dear.

01:25:43.934 --> 01:25:46.347
Now the stones are falling into place.

01:25:48.488 --> 01:25:51.661
What rock are you talking about?

01:25:52.099 --> 01:25:57.261
Say, to serve dolls like you, is not part of the job description.

01:25:57.598 --> 01:26:00.629
Find your own curier. Have a good day!

01:26:02.891 --> 01:26:04.166
Look at her.

01:26:16.055 --> 01:26:16.850
Doruk.

01:26:17.738 --> 01:26:18.830
Doruk, wake up.

01:26:19.266 --> 01:26:20.451
Wake up, Doruk.

01:26:20.923 --> 01:26:24.070
Mom, I feel asleep towards the morning, please let me sleep.

01:26:24.157 --> 01:26:27.610
Everything that happened to us is because you sleep every morning.

01:26:31.768 --> 01:26:33.073
What has happened to us?

01:26:33.427 --> 01:26:34.292
You do not see that, right?

01:26:36.258 --> 01:26:38.365
You look pretty good.

01:26:39.388 --> 01:26:42.060
Son, you're not aware of anything?

01:26:43.805 --> 01:26:50.049
Mother would it not be better if you put aside the questions and you talk more openly?

01:26:51.316 --> 01:26:57.997
Your brother is at work. Your dad is creating a program for his retirement and you're at home sleeping.

01:26:58.394 --> 01:26:59.455
Is that not great?

01:27:00.526 --> 01:27:03.145
Everything is in order. Perfect.

01:27:04.604 --> 01:27:10.184
You are going to get out of that bed immediately, take a shower and go to work.

01:27:10.350 --> 01:27:15.007
Doruk Look, you owe me this. I swear I will not tolerate this.

01:27:16.406 --> 01:27:18.060
Okay, okay, okay.

01:27:18.602 --> 01:27:19.468
Calm down.

01:27:21.546 --> 01:27:22.712
Just relax.

01:27:24.423 --> 01:27:26.198
Is it possible you're going through menopause?

01:27:26.973 --> 01:27:27.742
Doruk

01:27:28.015 --> 01:27:29.547
She probably has.

01:27:42.460 --> 01:27:46.645
The agent expects photos to tie to the magazine.

01:27:46.712 --> 01:27:47.945
Catalog, speed, agent, photographs.

01:27:53.445 --> 01:27:55.012
Why are you waiting here?

01:27:55.714 --> 01:27:58.848
If I say, for the bus, this conversation will extend.

01:28:05.963 --> 01:28:07.667
I'm waiting for a task.

01:28:08.955 --> 01:28:10.503
Why were you hired?

01:28:10.954 --> 01:28:13.019
To support your assistant.

01:28:13.301 --> 01:28:15.091
Then help my assistant.

01:28:29.452 --> 01:28:32.165
Did you tell the sector that we are looking for young designers?

01:28:32.262 --> 01:28:33.188
I advertised, sir.

01:28:35.024 --> 01:28:37.236
If I wanted advertising, I would have said.

01:28:39.332 --> 01:28:41.571
Advertising was not needed. He would have said so.

01:28:42.088 --> 01:28:45.143
I need experienced young designers.

01:28:46.183 --> 01:28:47.358
We know what we need.

01:28:47.712 --> 01:28:51.571
Look at the staff of the rival companies. Offer jobs.

01:28:51.761 --> 01:28:53.022
Are we going to steal staff?

01:29:05.520 --> 01:29:08.036
I mean, it is not shameful?

01:29:10.466 --> 01:29:13.611
In addition, why would they work for you if they already have good jobs?

01:29:17.344 --> 01:29:22.795
Ms. Cagla, please tell your assistant she's not here to question my orders, but to execute them.

01:29:24.021 --> 01:29:26.428
Because if she can't work without orders, she can at least listen.

01:29:28.265 --> 01:29:30.180
Don't question. Execute. Learn to listen.

01:29:33.686 --> 01:29:35.320
I wonder if he would die if I was to give him an order.

01:29:43.276 --> 01:29:44.700
What is the winter collection's situation?

01:29:44.705 --> 01:29:45.948
Designers are going to finish, sir.

01:29:46.281 --> 01:29:47.504
But we're still in June.

01:29:50.786 --> 01:29:51.982
What did I say?

01:29:52.397 --> 01:29:54.102
What is the winter collection's situation?

01:29:54.523 --> 01:29:59.082
What did I say along the way? Since you're not taking notes and questioning me, I think you rely on your memory too much.

01:30:07.196 --> 01:30:09.688
Did you tell the sector that we are looking for young designers?

01:30:09.885 --> 01:30:11.764
If I wanted advertising, I would have said.

01:30:12.064 --> 01:30:19.071
I need young designers and experienced staff . Research our rivals.

01:30:22.835 --> 01:30:24.813
Let little Miss make the adaptation process.

01:30:27.933 --> 01:30:28.714
What is that?

01:30:29.634 --> 01:30:36.410
In short, running from floor to floor jobs. Find Edil on the second floor, she will tell you what to do.

01:31:18.220 --> 01:31:27.496
I would have gave him a piece of my mind if I had not needed this job. I wonder how it would have been if I didn't have an influence from my 'father'. What a sadist.

01:31:28.700 --> 01:31:29.989
Watch where you're going.

01:31:30.461 --> 01:31:31.470
Was it just me?

01:31:32.786 --> 01:31:37.287
Excuse me, I got angry at someone else and took my anger out on you.

01:31:37.461 --> 01:31:40.250
Let me guess, the centre of your anger is from Murat Sarslimaz.

01:31:40.731 --> 01:31:44.070
Perfect guess. What strange person is he?

01:31:44.109 --> 01:31:47.134
I do not know what the problem is but he enjoys taking his anger out on others.

01:31:47.433 --> 01:31:52.419
He gains power through torture. It's a hard case. After examining him, it would take three years to diagnose his illness.

01:31:53.070 --> 01:31:55.297
Okay, so he's just like that at work.

01:31:56.222 --> 01:32:00.594
I don't think so. Whatever someone is, they will remain forever. Anyone who said else is a liar.

01:32:01.119 --> 01:32:04.550
Nobody said it, I speak from experience.

01:32:06.138 --> 01:32:07.794
You two are friends?

01:32:08.555 --> 01:32:09.681
Somehow.

01:32:11.764 --> 01:32:14.083
Please do not tell me that you are more than that, god forbid.

01:32:15.150 --> 01:32:16.941
It happens to be my big brother.

01:32:23.923 --> 01:32:25.467
See, this isn't good now.

01:32:25.955 --> 01:32:30.134
No, it's not a problem. Sometimes my brother deserves these words.

01:32:30.657 --> 01:32:32.925
Although, I congratulate you for your courage.

01:32:33.789 --> 01:32:35.119
Doruk Sarslimaz.

01:32:35.509 --> 01:32:37.877
Suna Pektas, but I like to use the name Hayat.

01:32:54.306 --> 01:32:56.597
How could two people be so different Ipek?

01:32:56.676 --> 01:32:58.389
How are they from the same parents?

01:32:58.970 --> 01:33:01.515
It isn't though. They have different mothers.

01:33:01.985 --> 01:33:08.266
One is actually a person, the other is a zoo escapee. I went up and down stairs because of him!

01:33:08.436 --> 01:33:09.756
Just think about the money?

01:33:10.332 --> 01:33:15.874
I will not get any money because I will quit. Mom is already back in town. I'll just look for another job.

01:33:16.068 --> 01:33:17.110
You can not find one.

01:33:17.404 --> 01:33:20.830
Girl, why you can not say something nice? I will find a job.

01:33:22.588 --> 01:33:29.680
If my name is Hayat Uzun, I will find another job.

01:33:30.100 --> 01:33:31.158
It's over.

01:33:31.777 --> 01:33:32.802
Go Hayat!

01:33:34.582 --> 01:33:35.729
Hayat go.

01:33:44.951 --> 01:33:46.263
Has Asli come home early?

01:33:46.460 --> 01:33:47.356
I don't know.

01:33:57.335 --> 01:33:58.418
Welcome.

01:34:01.596 --> 01:34:02.480
Mother?

01:34:03.418 --> 01:34:05.011
Did not you leave in the morning?

01:34:05.237 --> 01:34:12.709
Your father told me to stay. He said 'With that sharp tongue, no one will keep her for longer than a week.

01:34:12.993 --> 01:34:20.084
'Sit and wait. Either she will get fired, or have enough and quit. Then the next day you will get her and come'.

01:34:22.553 --> 01:34:23.783
He must have said it.

01:34:49.984 --> 01:34:53.238
Have a little mercy, look at how old I am.

01:34:53.954 --> 01:35:00.225
You could outrun everyone, Nejat Sarslimaz. We don't have mercy. Empathy? None.

01:35:01.585 --> 01:35:04.125
Look at this hooligan.

01:35:05.166 --> 01:35:07.667
Where did you learn this phrase?

01:35:07.787 --> 01:35:09.168
In "Hababam Sinifi".

01:35:10.975 --> 01:35:19.878
That film is all about you: mischief, diabolical luck, escaping from your job. Everything is there.

01:35:25.424 --> 01:35:27.615
Who's winning? I'll choose my side according to it.

01:35:28.659 --> 01:35:32.621
Come on son, your brother is beating me.

01:35:33.341 --> 01:35:35.562
Surprise me once, Nejat.

01:35:36.301 --> 01:35:40.505
But Dad, even with my brother, the results will not change.

01:35:41.216 --> 01:35:43.174
I can beat you both.

01:35:43.361 --> 01:35:46.813
Remember, Doruk, who laughs last, laughs best.

01:35:51.606 --> 01:35:53.633
You can not win every game.

01:35:54.327 --> 01:35:55.386
Pot.

01:36:03.382 --> 01:36:04.956
But it depends on one thing.

01:36:06.382 --> 01:36:08.286
What is it? I'm curious.

01:36:08.902 --> 01:36:11.319
Only if the winner is not my brother.

01:36:19.221 --> 01:36:24.120
Guys, then, whoever catches this one, wins.

01:36:29.595 --> 01:36:34.515
If the mother discovers what I've been doing, she would crush me like hazelnuts in shell, without any mercy.

01:36:35.874 --> 01:36:39.392
Frankly, my dear, I think you should tell the truth.

01:36:39.808 --> 01:36:45.643
I mean, when you explained in this morning, she was softer and listened to you.

01:36:46.525 --> 01:36:51.294
This is Aunt Emine. If you marinaded her in kindness for 3 days, she wouldn't soften.

01:36:51.613 --> 01:36:53.387
Who has died of sincerity?

01:36:53.954 --> 01:36:56.373
Truth can not always be said.

01:36:56.794 --> 01:37:01.941
Girls, don't start again. It doesn't matter if I tell or not, this will explode in my face someday.

01:37:02.880 --> 01:37:03.910
Exactly.

01:37:05.893 --> 01:37:06.872
It won't.

01:37:07.079 --> 01:37:11.268
The girl knows 4 languages! 4! My English is this: Alright, Okay, Yes, No.

01:37:12.036 --> 01:37:14.936
There isn't a place she hasn't been and I do not even have a passport.

01:37:16.688 --> 01:37:23.860
That human misery will not ask for anything but work anyway but if I face Mr Nejat, I don't know what I'd do.

01:37:24.448 --> 01:37:29.333
Plus, just looking at her social media will be enough.

01:37:29.564 --> 01:37:36.984
You're lucky that you don't have to get plastic surgery. She hasn't posted photo's of her online and any other accounts are private.

01:37:38.227 --> 01:37:42.887
You sly fox, for the past 2 hours, you've been inspecting her social media accounts?!

01:37:43.282 --> 01:37:46.518
Exactly. I think it's more useful than breaking nuts.

01:37:46.738 --> 01:37:48.926
I love you. Any other information?

01:37:49.484 --> 01:37:50.613
Well, I mean,

01:37:51.491 --> 01:37:55.588
from now on you are an animal lover and addicted to nature.

01:37:55.753 --> 01:37:58.504
Your accounts are full of wings and beaks.

01:38:01.001 --> 01:38:03.564
Girls, I don't think she has a normal brain.

01:38:05.389 --> 01:38:07.117
That is an unknown bird, Suna.

01:38:07.521 --> 01:38:10.314
We must see it.

01:38:10.752 --> 01:38:16.268
It comes once every five years and stays for only 3 days. It is so unknown that it doesn't have a name.

01:38:17.092 --> 01:38:20.329
There is only one thing I know: I'm finished.

01:38:20.726 --> 01:38:22.965
How do I tell my father that I did not get the job.

01:38:24.551 --> 01:38:26.760
Maybe you should leave him a voicemail.

01:38:27.506 --> 01:38:30.645
So far, I lived after my father's wishes.

01:38:31.140 --> 01:38:38.645
But I've had enough. Just to teach me a lesson, he sent me with that resume for a job as an assistant.

01:38:39.438 --> 01:38:43.671
I'm going to go now and tell him 'It's up to here.' Let him be upset a bit.

01:38:43.671 --> 01:38:44.739
But he has a heart ..

01:38:44.739 --> 01:38:46.332
No, Gokce, he has no heart.

01:38:49.900 --> 01:38:56.511
What about my heart broken, Gokce? Who will think of it? This matter will be closed tonight.

01:39:08.328 --> 01:39:09.173
Murat.

01:39:10.062 --> 01:39:13.399
I want back the calories that I've burned.

01:39:13.629 --> 01:39:17.448
This thing known as sports makes me gain weight, son.

01:39:18.235 --> 01:39:21.497
I'm as hungry as a fox again. What should we make?

01:39:21.962 --> 01:39:25.829
Later, okay, Dad? I go home now and get ready for an important meeting tomorrow.

01:39:26.440 --> 01:39:27.780
I waited to tell you goodbye.

01:39:28.082 --> 01:39:32.954
Don't go, son. Let work wait. Can life pass like this?

01:39:33.261 --> 01:39:34.225
Work can wait?

01:39:34.941 --> 01:39:37.824
Mr. Nejat, work can't wait, I learnt that from you.

01:39:39.114 --> 01:39:43.243
That is true, but when you're older, your priorities change, son.

01:39:44.299 --> 01:39:46.233
Therefore, I must retire.

01:39:47.319 --> 01:39:53.107
Alright, leave. But, I was going to call Kemal. Maybe you'd like to talk to him before you leave.

01:39:53.597 --> 01:39:55.982
You can share your observations about his daughter in front of him.

01:39:56.460 --> 01:40:01.111
It is better if I don't, trust me. Plus you know I don't like to lie.

01:40:01.355 --> 01:40:03.148
So the situation is so bad to explain.

01:40:04.126 --> 01:40:07.333
The girl just started and her resume is good.

01:40:08.483 --> 01:40:12.911
Well, her first performance showed me that I keep my expectations.

01:40:14.124 --> 01:40:15.418
Now excuse me, I gotta go.

01:40:15.562 --> 01:40:16.501
OK Bye.

01:40:17.142 --> 01:40:17.887
But..

01:40:19.685 --> 01:40:22.938
Stay true to your word, you've me promised a meal.

01:40:25.903 --> 01:40:29.347
And I am aware that the student has become the master, Murat.

01:40:30.784 --> 01:40:33.863
I am proud of you, don't forget this.

01:40:42.154 --> 01:40:48.961
My pride, my picture of contentment, I can not tell you how proud I am as a father.

01:40:49.340 --> 01:40:50.177
Dad, I...

01:40:50.409 --> 01:40:57.427
No, no, my child. My little daughter has grown up and got a job!

01:40:57.570 --> 01:40:58.766
Yes, work well ..

01:40:58.868 --> 01:41:00.484
You love it, right?

01:41:00.564 --> 01:41:02.550
Textiles; it's a colored sector?

01:41:04.360 --> 01:41:05.374
Father.

01:41:05.559 --> 01:41:06.524
We have to talk.

01:41:12.220 --> 01:41:16.949
Look who's calling, your uncle Nejat.

01:41:20.225 --> 01:41:21.720
Nejat, how are you?

01:41:22.574 --> 01:41:28.297
Thank you. Suna and I were just talking about you.

01:41:29.782 --> 01:41:33.418
Very nice, very nice.

01:41:35.084 --> 01:41:42.611
Look, that's good, now I feel relieved. I'll arrange it before I leave. Take care.

01:41:46.640 --> 01:41:47.893
Did you not get upset?

01:41:48.222 --> 01:41:49.764
On the contrary, I am happy.

01:41:50.634 --> 01:41:52.796
Nejat uncle liked you.

01:41:52.967 --> 01:41:54.014
Nejat uncle...

01:41:54.791 --> 01:41:55.672
Me?

01:41:55.795 --> 01:42:03.456
He said that I grew a fine, respecting little girl. He was really happy with your chat, by the way.

01:42:03.664 --> 01:42:05.452
Our chat?

01:42:05.653 --> 01:42:07.349
Yes, you spoke in the morning.

01:42:20.526 --> 01:42:26.614
I have to go for 30 minutes and until I get back, stay away from important things. Answer the phone, but make no promises.

01:42:29.614 --> 01:42:31.863
And Mr Murat wants to see you, I'm late.

01:42:36.982 --> 01:42:39.982
Let's hope for the best

01:42:54.116 --> 01:42:57.356
It won't take long. Once I find out what is going on, I'll come back.

01:42:57.467 --> 01:43:00.270
What could be going on, dear, maybe your dad misunderstood.

01:43:00.566 --> 01:43:05.921
I left without encountering anyone, so who is that person who has met with Nejat uncle?

01:43:08.074 --> 01:43:10.377
Yes, it is a little odd.

01:43:10.492 --> 01:43:13.030
I will return after I solve the mystery.

01:43:23.209 --> 01:43:24.002
Enter.

01:43:27.232 --> 01:43:28.199
Take this.

01:43:29.443 --> 01:43:30.340
What is this?

01:43:31.465 --> 01:43:33.465
I don't know, I mean, it looks like a key to me.

01:43:34.380 --> 01:43:36.937
I understood that much. I meant what am I supposed to do with it?

01:43:38.666 --> 01:43:43.271
Oh, but I guess, it opens doors.

01:44:48.765 --> 01:44:51.435
This is the key for the archive where old creations are stored.

01:44:53.079 --> 01:44:54.229
So will it stay with me?

01:44:54.724 --> 01:44:55.831
No, you will stay there.

01:44:56.806 --> 01:45:00.236
So after yesterday's torture with the stairs, 
am I going to organise shelves?

01:45:00.454 --> 01:45:04.431
Its interesting how you see labor as punishment. 
I recommend seeing a therapist.

01:45:22.941 --> 01:45:24.689
I came to see Suna Pektas.

01:45:24.875 --> 01:45:28.144
I saw her going into Mr Murat's office. 
You can wait here if you want.

01:45:28.369 --> 01:45:29.391
Okay, thank you.

01:45:45.650 --> 01:45:46.916
You have to organize the archive.

01:45:47.358 --> 01:45:48.125
Organize?

01:45:49.901 --> 01:45:52.354
Maybe you should see an aurist after therapy.

01:45:53.969 --> 01:45:57.812
Drawings in the first 20 years are in documents.
Transfer them on to the the system.

01:45:58.280 --> 01:45:59.175
One by one?

01:45:59.677 --> 01:46:01.266
If you can, take ten out of ten.

01:46:05.945 --> 01:46:07.724
What is your problem with me?

01:46:08.889 --> 01:46:11.216
Well, I know my father said show me mercy.

01:46:12.787 --> 01:46:15.044
This has nothing to do with your father.

01:46:15.880 --> 01:46:18.058
So you're saying that this is your overall attitude.

01:46:18.578 --> 01:46:22.559
Look, I don't see a problem and when it comes 
to work I have only one attitude: professionalism.

01:46:23.440 --> 01:46:26.303
If you want to be my assistant, you should know what work is.

01:46:26.750 --> 01:46:30.071
I tell you enter files into a system, but you have absolutely no idea about it.

01:46:31.619 --> 01:46:34.120
I repeat: do not ask, execute.

01:46:38.608 --> 01:46:39.406
Fine.

01:46:50.812 --> 01:46:53.602
Do not ask, execute. You have no idea about the world of work.

01:46:53.761 --> 01:46:56.513
You have no idea how to be human, what we do?

01:46:57.114 --> 01:46:59.543
I'm not an assistant here, I'm withstanding torture!

01:46:59.859 --> 01:47:01.709
He is not the boss, he is a demon from hell.

01:47:02.436 --> 01:47:06.166
What evil did I do to get into the hands of this creature?

01:47:06.748 --> 01:47:10.049
Suna probably felt it, that's why she left.

01:47:11.922 --> 01:47:12.602
Hi.

01:47:13.226 --> 01:47:14.772
I came to see my Pektas Call.

01:47:15.216 --> 01:47:16.223
I am Suna Pektas.

01:47:26.402 --> 01:47:28.378
What a coincidence, so am I.

01:47:38.617 --> 01:47:39.649
Miss Suna?

01:47:39.807 --> 01:47:40.606
Yes?

01:47:43.484 --> 01:47:59.908
Translation: serialeturcestitraduse